creasing pressure to prove their value to a company and to show ROI on all marketing campaigns, including offline?By Natasha Fourie 9 Jul 2019The ultimate goal set forward by Egta and The Global TV Group is to build a solid foundation for the TV industry to move forward in unison – evolving audience measurement, setting the highest standards allowing for comparability on a global level and building bridges with industry stakeholders in an increasingly digital, multi-screen and cross-platform advertising landscape.Read the TV Charter here.